#Text=Wikinews interviews Irene Villa
#Text=Tuesday , February 26 , 2013
#Text=Irene
#Text=Villa after the interview with the Wikinews reporters .
#Text=Image : Raystorm .
#Text=Yesterday evening in La Molina , Spain , Wikinews sat down and talked with Irene Villa to discuss para-alpine skiing , disability sport , women 's sport , and her own sporting career .
#Text=Villa was in town as part of activities taking place around the 2013 IPC Alpine World Championships , where one of her skiing club teammates is competing as a member of the Spanish team .
#Text=Her high profile in Spain has brought additional interest to para-alpine skiing and disability sport in general .
#Text=( ( Wikinews ) ) :
#Text=Hi we are interviewing Irene Villa , who is a disability skier from Spain and professional author , social figure , journalist , and psychologist .
#Text=You are most well known for being a terrorist survivor , but you 're here because of the [ 2013 Alpine Skiing ] World Championships . ( ( es))Spanish language :

#Text=‍Hola estamos entrevistando a Irene Villa , esquiadora española , escritora , figura política , psicóloga y periodista . Aunque se le conoce más por haber sobrevivido a un atentado , se encuentra aquí por el Campeonato del Mundo [ de Esquí Adaptado 2013 ] .
#Text=Irene Villa : I 'm here because I love sitting ski , I practice and I compete , but since I got pregnant and my son was born I stopped competing .
#Text=But before I had my son I competed against the people who will run tomorrow , the Germans who win , and I wanted to be here .
#Text=I have n't raced in the World Cup , but I did race in the European Cup .
#Text=And well , I 'm also here to support paralympic sports . ( ( es))Spanish language :

#Text=‍Estoy aquí porque me encanta el esquí en silla , lo practico y he competido , pero desde que nació mi hijo dejé de competir , porque me quedé embarazada , pero antes de tener a mi hijo competí contra las que mañana corren , las alemanas que ganan , y quería estar aquí .
#Text=Nunca Copa del Mundo , he corrido Copa de Europa .
#Text=Y bueno , para apoyar al deporte paralímpico .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) : In 2009 you said you were trying to make the 2010 Winter Paralympics .

#Text=After giving birth are you going to continue with the sport and hope to make 2018 ? ( ( es))Spanish language : ‍En 2009 dijo que quería clasificarse para los Juegos Paralímpicos de Invierno de 2010 .
#Text=Tras dar a luz , ¿ va a continuar con el deporte e intentar llegar a 2018 ?
#Text=Irene Villa :
#Text=I would love to .
#Text=The thing is that you need a certain amount of IPCAS points .
#Text=I 'm now competing , on top of that I have an injury , tomorrow and the next day I will be training , and I do n't know if I 'll have enough time to make it .

#Text=Sochi [ Winter Paralympic Games of 2014 ] is right around the corner , next year , so it depends on how many point you 've got . 2018 ? For sure . ( ( es))Spanish language : ‍Me encantaría . Lo que pasa que bueno , eso no se sabe , porque tienes que tener unos puntos IPCAS determinados y yo ahora estoy compitiendo , encima me he lesionado , y mañana y pasado voy a estar esquiando , y no sé si van a dar los tiempos para llegar ...
#Text=Es que Sochi [ Juegos Paralímpicos de 2014 ] está aquí al lado .
#Text=Son el año que viene .
#Text=Entonces depende de los puntos IPCAS que tengas . ¿ 2018 ? Seguro que sí .
